description: Stone Valley stretches below you, burying itself in the twin peaks of Thanatoph to the southeast.  Carried on a gentle breeze, the sweet smell of wildflowers drifts up from the moonlit valley below.  A worn trail wends its way southeast into the valley through a row of elderberry brambles.

Stone Valley stretches below you, burying itself in the twin peaks of Thanatoph to the southeast.  Bright patches of wildflowers dot the valley below and their sweet smell is carried on a gentle breeze.  A worn trail wends its way southeast into the valley through a row of elderberry brambles.
title: [Thanatoph, Stone Valley]
